    Overview

    Details

    Player: One is built by our gaming PC experts with premium gaming components to give you a competitive advantage. Player: One makes a great starter PC and has plenty of room for upgrades.

    • Windows 11 Home
    • NVIDIA® GeForce RTX™ 3050 GPU - 6GB or NVIDIA® GeForce RTX™ 4060 GPU
    • Intel® Core™ i5-13400F or AMD Ryzen™ 5 8400F
    • 16GB or 32GB DDR5 5200 MHz RAM
    • 1TB or 2TB NVMe M.2 SSD storage space
    • Get 1080p Gaming Performance
    • Real-time ray tracing technology
    • Air cooled with NZXT 120
    • 80 Plus Gold power supplies for lower power consumption
    • Overclockable GPU options to unlock higher frame rates (Use at your own risk. See terms for full info)
    • Solid Single Threaded Performance to execute simultaneous processes

    Reviews

    Questions And Answers

    FAQs

    The CPU is like the brain of your build, coordinating all components for your PC to run and impacting in-game FPS.

    Intel® Core™ i7-13700KF:

    • Top-tier option
    • Allows overclocking for enhanced speed
    • Features more cores and threads for superior multitasking
    • Delivers higher performance for demanding applications and games

    Intel® Core™ i5-13400F:

    • Cost-effective choice
    • Provides reliable performance for most tasks
    • Does not support overclocking, meaning speed is fixed
    • Ideal for everyday gaming and computing without extra frills

    AMD Ryzen 5 8400F

    • Mid-range option
    • Provides balanced performance for gaming and multitasking
    • Requires a discrete GPU for video output
    • Supports overclocking for improved performance when needed

    GPU, also known as "graphics card," is responsible for displaying images, animations, and graphics on your computer's screen. A more powerful GPU enhances game performance, making games run faster and appear more visually appealing.

    NVIDIA® GeForce RTX™ 4060:

    • Higher-tier GPU
    • Provides more power and performance enhancements
    • Ideal for demanding gaming and creative tasks

    NVIDIA® GeForce RTX™ 3050:

    • Mid-range GPU
    • Suitable for standard gaming and tasks

    RAM is crucial for running applications and games on your PC. It stores temporary data to help your PC manage multiple tasks at once. More RAM enables better multitasking and responsiveness.

    RAM
    16GBIdeal for casual gaming and standard office tasks, ensuring smooth performance and multitasking.
    32GBNecessary for dedicated gaming or resource-heavy tasks like video editing, providing ample power for demanding software.
    64GBBest for high-end gaming at maximum settings, complex 3D modeling, and editing high-resolution photos and videos.

    Your storage device holds the operating system, applications, and files, with speeds measured in MB/s (Megabytes per Second). Faster storage retrieves information more quickly.

    StorageCapacity for AAA GamesUse Case
    500GB5 to 10Casual gamers with a select few games
    1TB10 to 20Avid gamers needing space for games, updates
    2TB20 to 40Gamers with extensive libraries and additional media
    4TB40 to 80Game developers and content creators with large files

    The graphics card shown in the product photos is for demonstration purposes only and may vary from the product received.
